  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "62c819195a83f70023e0bf41",
      "text": "Scrapbox Golf",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280803,
      "updated": 1657280803
    },
    {
      "id": "62c8192379d3a9000017c5f5",
      "text": "[ScrapGames#6279ecd855cbd30000f61474]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280803,
      "updated": 1657280803
    },
    {
      "id": "62c8192379d3a9000017c5f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280803,
      "updated": 1657280812
    },
    {
      "id": "62c8192c79d3a9000017c5f8",
      "text": "[書いてけ]レベルで継続的に遊びやすそうと思った[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280812,
      "updated": 1657280887
    },
    {
      "id": "62c8194379d3a9000017c5f9",
      "text": " いや、人を選びそうか……",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280836,
      "updated": 1657280890
    },
    {
      "id": "62c8194779d3a9000017c5fa",
      "text": " ゴルフはしなくても「どれが一番わかりやすい投票する」楽しみ方もあるかも",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280839,
      "updated": 1657280865
    },
    {
      "id": "62c8192379d3a9000017c5f6",
      "text": "\tあとは、わかりにくい概念の説明を噛み砕いてほしい人がゴルフネタとして持ち込むとか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280803,
      "updated": 1657280911
    },
    {
      "id": "62c8198f79d3a9000017c5fc",
      "text": "\t\tその人はわかりやすい説明が手に入る",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280911,
      "updated": 1657280916
    },
    {
      "id": "62c8199379d3a9000017c5fd",
      "text": "\t\tGolferたちは遊べる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280916,
      "updated": 1657280922
    },
    {
      "id": "62c8199979d3a9000017c5fe",
      "text": "\t\twin-win！？",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280922,
      "updated": 1657280928
    },
    {
      "id": "62c8197c79d3a9000017c5fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1657280893,
      "updated": 1776500389
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b19e",
      "text": "from [ScrapGames]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b19f",
      "text": "[Scrapbox Golf]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1a0",
      "text": " [長く美しい文章]のお題があり、それをScrapboxでどれだけ簡潔にまとめられるか",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1a1",
      "text": " 　Scrapboxのライティング練習になる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1a2",
      "text": " 　[頭にスッと入ってくる箇条書きの構成方法]の練習になる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1a3",
      "text": " [CodeGolf]や[VimGolf]のScrapbox版を意識した",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1a4",
      "text": " 例",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1a5",
      "text": "  code:お題",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1a6",
      "text": "   赤血球は血液細胞の一つで色は赤く血液循環によって体中を回り、肺から得た酸素を取り込み、体の隅々の細胞に運び供給する役割を担い、また同様に二酸化炭素の排出も行う。赤血球の内部には鉄を含む赤いタンパク質ヘモグロビンが充満しており、赤血球はヘモグロビンに酸素を取り込む",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1a7",
      "text": "  回答例",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1a8",
      "text": "  　赤血球",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1a9",
      "text": "  　　血液細胞の一つ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1aa",
      "text": "  　　赤い",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1ab",
      "text": "  　　　鉄を含む赤いタンパク質ヘモグロビンが充満しているため",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1ac",
      "text": "  　　血液循環によって体中を回り、以下の機能を担う",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1ad",
      "text": "  　　　酸素の供給",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1ae",
      "text": "  　　　　肺から得た酸素を体の隅々の細胞に供給する",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1af",
      "text": "  　　　　ヘモグロビンに酸素を取り込む",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1b0",
      "text": "  　 　二酸化炭素の排出",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1b1",
      "text": "\t\t\t[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1b2",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t赤血球:血液細胞の一つ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1b3",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t役割: 体の隅々の細胞に  酸素を供給 / 二酸化炭素を排出",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1b4",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t内部にヘモグロビンが充満",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1b5",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t[* 鉄]を含むタンパク質→赤い",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1b6",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t酸素を取り込む",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1b7",
      "text": "\t\t\t[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1b8",
      "text": "    赤血球とは",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1b9",
      "text": "    \t血液細胞の一つ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1ba",
      "text": "   \t役割は二つ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1bb",
      "text": "   \t\t身体の隅々に酸素を運ぶこと",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1bc",
      "text": "   \t\t身体の二酸化炭素を排出すること",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1bd",
      "text": "   \t構造",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1be",
      "text": "   \t\t赤血球/",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1bf",
      "text": "   \t\t\t鉄/",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1c0",
      "text": "   \t\t\tヘモグロビン/",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1c1",
      "text": "   \t\t\t\t★酸素はコイツに保存してから運ぶ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1c2",
      "text": "   [wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1c3",
      "text": "   \t赤血球",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1c4",
      "text": "    \t血液細胞の一つ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1c5",
      "text": "     内部には[* 鉄]を含む赤いタンパク質 ヘモグロビンが充満",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1c6",
      "text": "     \t赤色",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1c7",
      "text": "      酸素を取り込む",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1c8",
      "text": "    \t血液循環によって体中を回る",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1c9",
      "text": "     \t役割：肺から得た酸素を取り込み体の隅々の細胞に運び供給する",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1ca",
      "text": "      \t二酸化炭素の排出も行う",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1cb",
      "text": "\t\t\t[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1776504747
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34fab0000000000a6ba36",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t赤血球",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776504748,
      "updated": 1776504752
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350410000000000a6ba42",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t血液細胞",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776504897,
      "updated": 1776504897
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350410000000000a6ba43",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t循環により体中を回る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776504897,
      "updated": 1776504897
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350be0000000000a6ba48",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tヘモグロビン（タンパク質）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505023,
      "updated": 1776505023
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350c20000000000a6ba4b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t酸素を取り込む",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505027,
      "updated": 1776505027
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3502b0000000000a6ba41",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t鉄",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776504876,
      "updated": 1776505001
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350c00000000000a6ba49",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t赤",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505024,
      "updated": 1776505024
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34fce0000000000a6ba3a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t酸素",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776504783,
      "updated": 1776504827
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350480000000000a6ba44",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t肺から得る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776504905,
      "updated": 1776504972
    },
    {
      "id": "69e34fe50000000000a6ba3c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t体中の細胞に供給",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776504806,
      "updated": 1776504842
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350090000000000a6ba3e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t二酸化炭素",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776504842,
      "updated": 1776504849
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350100000000000a6ba3f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t排出（多分酸素の逆）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776504849,
      "updated": 1776504866
    },
    {
      "id": "69e352990000000000a6ba5f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t……木じゃない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505498,
      "updated": 1776505507
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350da0000000000a6ba4c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tcode:mermaid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505051,
      "updated": 1776505057
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350e20000000000a6ba4d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t graph",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505059,
      "updated": 1776505061
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350e50000000000a6ba4e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 赤血球-->血液細胞",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505062,
      "updated": 1776505079
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350f80000000000a6ba4f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 赤血球-->循環-->体中を回る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505080,
      "updated": 1776505092
    },
    {
      "id": "69e351040000000000a6ba50",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 赤血球-->ヘモグロビン",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505092,
      "updated": 1776505099
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3510c0000000000a6ba51",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t ヘモグロビン-->|取り込む|酸素",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505101,
      "updated": 1776505126
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3512b0000000000a6ba52",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t ヘモグロビン-->鉄",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505132,
      "updated": 1776505137
    },
    {
      "id": "69e351310000000000a6ba53",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t ヘモグロビン-->赤",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505138,
      "updated": 1776505144
    },
    {
      "id": "69e351a50000000000a6ba58",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 酸化鉄-.-赤",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505253,
      "updated": 1776505398
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3520c0000000000a6ba5b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 酸化鉄-.-酸素",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505356,
      "updated": 1776505403
    },
    {
      "id": "69e352190000000000a6ba5d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 酸化鉄-.-鉄",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505370,
      "updated": 1776505407
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3521a0000000000a6ba5e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 鉄イオン-.-赤",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505370,
      "updated": 1776505410
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3520c0000000000a6ba5c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 酸素-->|得る|肺",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505356,
      "updated": 1776505370
    },
    {
      "id": "69e351550000000000a6ba56",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 酸素-->|供給|体中を回る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505174,
      "updated": 1776505185
    },
    {
      "id": "69e351490000000000a6ba55",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 二酸化炭素-->|放出?|肺",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505162,
      "updated": 1776505206
    },
    {
      "id": "69e351850000000000a6ba57",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t 二酸化炭素-->|受取?|体中を回る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776505222,
      "updated": 1776505243
    },
    {
      "id": "69e350210000000000a6ba40",
      "text": "  Wikipediaのトップにあったものから適当に引っ張ってきたがいい例かも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776504866,
      "updated": 1776504915
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1cd",
      "text": "  　ヘモグロビンの記述が赤さと酸素供給に関わるので構造自体を変えるともっとうまくいきそう",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1ce",
      "text": "  　　そしてヘモグロビンでまとめようとすると二酸化炭素の運搬にヘモグロビンがどれくらい関わっているのかについて調べる必要がありやはりなかなか難しい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1cf",
      "text": "  ルール決めないといけないな",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1d0",
      "text": "  　自分の言葉で書き直していいのか",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1d1",
      "text": " おもしろい[inajob.icon][takker.icon][sta.icon][wogikaze.icon][meganii.icon][hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1776503643
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1d2",
      "text": " \t[Kozaneba]を使うと良いかも",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1d3",
      "text": " \tむしろKozanebaの宣伝になりそう[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1d4",
      "text": " \t 受けて立つぞい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1d5",
      "text": " [アクティブ読書]でよくやるやつだ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "654eade25e90c0000039b1d6",
      "text": "\tどう取捨選択してどうまとめるかに個性が出て面白い[sta.icon*2]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699655139,
      "updated": 1699655139
    },
    {
      "id": "69e365fe000000000023b4b2",
      "text": "\tガーティックフォンみたいに美文→箇条書き→美文→箇条書き…でリレーしていって最後の人の美文と最初の美文を比べるみたくすると協力ゲーム要素が生まれて楽しそう[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776510462,
      "updated": 1776510533
    },
